y-burgos/B_0153_L_1.webp","w":725,"h":900,"caption":"TOLEDO","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":13,"place_id":"madrid-spain","lon":-3.703507,"lat":40.416782,"place":"Madrid, Spain","date":"2008-07-27","role":"overnight_base","quote":"just before midnight we went to a bar, to give Charles (+ us!) a bowl of gazpacho + a sort of omlette!","images":[{"src":"media/2008-spain-france-2008-bilbao-ferry-burgos/B_0154_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":820,"caption":"The Family of Carlos IV, Goya, Prado","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2008-spain-france-2008-bilbao-ferry-burgos/B_0155_L_1.webp","w":520,"h":900,"caption":"Zurbarán still life with 4 vases 1658-64, Prado","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":14,"place_id":"embalse-de-la-cuerda-del-pozo-soria-spain","lon":-2.7237711,"lat":41.8658549,"place":"Embalse de la Cuerda del Pozo, Soria, Spain","date":"2008-07-27","role":"overnight_base","quote":"I swam (Simon + Charles paddled) in the enormous lake.","images":[]},{"seq":15,"place_id":"laguna-negra-soria-spain","lon":-2.8462481,"lat":41.9985617,"place":"Laguna Negra, Soria, Spain","date":"2008-07-27","role":"transit_stop","quote":"Someone has written a poem about it. Really lovely.","images":[]},{"seq":16,"place_id":"santa-maria-de-eunate-navarre-spain","lon":-1.761504,"lat":42.6722283,"place":"Santa Maria de Eunate, Navarre, Spain","date":"2008-07-27","role":"transit_stop","quote":"We stopped at St. Maria Eurate (again) on the pilgrimage route. There's a stone colonnade around it.","images":[]},{"seq":17,"place_id":"pamplona-spain","lon":-1.6522353,"lat":42.815686,"place":"Pamplona, Spain","date":"2008-07-27","role":"overnight_base","quote":"It's about the best campsite we've been in.","images":[]},{"seq":18,"place_id":"sorauren-navarre-spain","lon":-1.6087724,"lat":42.8682998,"place":"Sorauren, Navarre, Spain","date":"2008-07-27","role":"main_stop","quote":"Charles wandered out to the loo in his Boxers. A very cross French camper shouted \"Silence!\"","images":[]},{"seq":19,"place_id":"roncesvalles-n